<l>ūṇuṭai yecca muyirkkellām vēṟalla</l>
<l>nāṇuṭaimai māntar ciṟappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Food, clothing and the like are common to all men but modesty is peculiar to the good.</l>
